Package: iftp
Title: Inverse First-Passage Time Problem and N-Branching Markov Process
    Simulations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Alexander", "Klump", , "alexander.klump@posteo.de",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simulation tools for the inverse first-passage time problem
    (IFTP) and N-branching Markov process (N-BMP). Implements three IFTP
    boundary approximation algorithms (Anulova discretization, quantile
    discretization, and soft-killing IFPT), particle system simulations
    (N-BMP and quantile thinning particle system), and an interactive Shiny application for
    exploring results. Based on Klump & Savov (2025), Klump (2023), Klump &
    Kolb (2024), De Masi et al. (2019), and Bérard & Frénais (2023).
